queries.query:
from(bucket: "metrics")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "network_data")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "network_data")
  |> drop(columns: ["request_id", "api_key",   "ip_address", "user_agent"])  
  |> group(columns: ["model_key"], mode:"by")  
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 12h, fn: count, createEmpty:false)  
  |> yield(name: "mean")
